#CHIP Y8950
#CLOCK 3579545

; Y8950 (OPL + ADPCM) OPL Core Test
;
; The Y8950 is essentially a YM3526 (OPL) with added ADPCM playback.
; This test validates the OPL core functionality, which should be
; comparable to the OPL2 (YM3812) reference.
;
; Tests:
; - All 9 OPL channels with 2-operator FM synthesis
; - Comparison to OPL2 reference behavior
; - Envelope tracking

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 1-3: Melody line
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Channel 4-6: Harmony (thirds)
e4 . f4 . g4 .

r4

; Channel 7-9: Bass line
c3 . . d3 . . e3 .

r4

; All 9 channels together
c4 & e4 & c3 .

r4

; Envelope test: long sustained notes to hear ADSR
c4 _ _ _ d4 _ _ _

r2

#END
